name: CI Global Asset Allocation Private Pool
longDescription: This funds objective is to achieve longterm capital growth by investing primarily in a broadly diversified portfolio of American equity securities.The portfolio advisor invests primarily in common shares of larger U.S. companies uses a disciplined value style. The portfolio advisor focuses on companies that are considered undervalued in relation to their future prospects and offer good absolute and relative value as characterized by measures such as lower than average pricebook and priceearnings. securities of countries and companies located anywhere in the world.
